reviewText: I would not waste my money on this video combo again.  It portrays the entire state of Florida with all the enthusiasm of a glorified rest home.  If I had not already been to Florida many times and known what it's really like, I would most likely be having second thoughts about visiting Florida after viewing this video.  The photography is bad and the background music puts you to sleep.  If I could do it again, I'd look around and find something better to spend my money on.
